OL,6,     GHuddersfield animal hospital
OL,7,     Gheads into war-torn Ukraine in an
OL,8,     Gambulance loaded with medical
OL,9,     Gsupplies. And a duck with penis
OL,10,     Gproblems might need an amputation.
OL,11,G0210FCruising with Jane McDonald
OL,12,     GStarting in Vancouver, Jane
OL,13,     Gcruises around Alaska, enjoying a
OL,14,     Gdog sledding adventure on an ice
OL,15,     Gfield and visiting the Glacier
OL,16,     GBay National Park en route.
